openclaw-local-bridge-macos
===========================

This project is a macOS/launchd port of openclaw-local-bridge.

It also bundles claude-max-api-proxy as a vendored dependency under
vendor/claude-max-api-proxy/.

Both upstream projects are MIT-licensed; their copyrights and license texts
are reproduced below and inside vendor/claude-max-api-proxy/LICENSE.

